{"tid":1259963,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"告急！！！29號自動通過 海濱要變做軍事碼頭！！！","createTime":"2019-06-26T17:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T13:00:18.000Z","uid":37055,"like":110,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"099a6f4289c1b7d81b79befe17e49a602a68ec94","tid":1259963,"uid":37055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:22:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s6DoyOJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs6DoyOJ.png&h=5ad24a7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係好知發生咩事既巴打麻煩睇睇呢幾條link<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200706/06/P200706060179.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F200706%2F06%2FP200706060179.htm&d=DodTvzQjJx20NomtZcTkruQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=da543158\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200706/06/P200706060179.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20130419/18233258\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20130419%2F18233258&d=DodTvzQjJx20NomtZcTkruQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=88d89e23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20130419%2F18233258&h=2c4c6106\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20130419/18233258</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/政情/345053/議員促廢除中環海濱變軍事碼頭議案-朱凱廸-否則會有示威抗議\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85%2F345053%2F%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E4%BF%83%E5%BB%A2%E9%99%A4%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0%E6%B5%B7%E6%BF%B1%E8%AE%8A%E8%BB%8D%E4%BA%8B%E7%A2%BC%E9%A0%AD%E8%AD%B0%E6%A1%88-%E6%9C%B1%E5%87%B1%E5%BB%B8-%E5%90%A6%E5%89%87%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%89%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0&d=DodTvzQjJx20NomtZcTkruQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=c3e4272b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/政情/345053/議員促廢除中環海濱變軍事碼頭議案-朱凱廸-否則會有示威抗議</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1994&nbsp;<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中英兩國訂立《軍事用地協議》，列明在中環新填海區預留150米海岸線作回歸後興建「軍用碼頭」，但<span style=\"font-size: large;\">並無提及</span>在中環海濱劃出「軍事用地」。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2000<br />\n政府制訂首份涵蓋中環新填海區的規劃圖，將中環海濱全部劃作「休憩用地」，<span style=\"color: red;\">只在海岸線上標明「軍事碼頭(有待詳細設計) 」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n2002&nbsp;<br />\n政府向立法會就中區填海計劃申請撥款，包括興建軍用碼頭所需款項，但<span style=\"color: red;\">從未提及在中環海濱劃出「軍事用地」</span>。此後政府一直承諾「還港於民」，中環海濱向市民開放，碼頭只供解放軍間歇使用。<br />\n<br />\n2011&nbsp;<br />\n政府完成《中環新海濱城市設計研究》，包括軍用碼頭設計，在年底向立法會匯報。<br />\n<br />\n2012&nbsp;<br />\n政府於年初第七次修訂中區規劃圖，仍然將中環海濱全部劃作「休憩用地」。<span style=\"color: red;\">在未獲城規會批准的情況下，於年底動工興建四座軍用碼頭設施。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2013<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">從未諮詢公眾的情況下</span>，政府於2月15日刊憲，把中環海濱三萬多平方呎核心地段永久劃作「軍事用地」。4月21日，陳茂波在網誌上首次披露政府會將碼頭移交解放軍管理，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">意味中環海濱的核心地段將由解放軍按照《註軍法》而非本港法律管轄</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n騙地謊言 Government's five deadly sins<br />\n<br />\n1. 曲解協議<br />\n中英協議只要求英方在香港回歸時預留150米海岸線興建軍用碼頭，但<span style=\"color: red;\">梁振英政府卻曲解為劃出三萬多平方呎<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">永久</span>軍事用地給解放軍管轄</span>。<br />\n<br />\n2. 亂搬龍門<br />\n自2000年起政府規劃圖一直將中環海濱劃作休憩用地，<span style=\"color: red;\">陳茂波今年二月突然改劃作軍事用地卻聲稱已諮詢多年</span>，反指市民搬龍門。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 違反承諾<br />\n政府為了在中區填海，一直聲稱還港於民，建設世界級海濱，<span style=\"color: red;\">現在卻違反承諾以解放軍優先，更違反城規條例和保護海港條例的精神</span>。<br />\n<br />\n4. 公權盡喪<br />\n政府聲稱軍事用地會在部分時段開放給公眾使用，即使實行，<span style=\"color: red;\">市民在中環海濱喪失公民權利，任何活動或集會均需經解放軍批准。</span><br />\n<br />\n5. 法網陷阱<br />\n根據中央頒佈的《駐軍法》，解放軍執行職務時不受香港法院管轄，所以中環海濱的軍事用地隨時會變成陷阱，令市民誤墮「大陸法網」，無法得到香港法律保障。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日唔覺唔覺忙緊嘅時候俾佢休咗會 <span style=\"color: green;\">搞到29號自動通過</span><br />\n幫幫手 香港人真係好唔得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42fa161299446d1aea4e23ab0b8952a3fa693c43","tid":1259963,"uid":37055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:28:20.000Z","msg":"我啲嘢都係係入面cope 見冇咩人出post 但真係好告急 <br />\n！！！！<br />\n<br />\n［立會直播post2］建制派休會辯論碼頭, 及投票星期六活動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1258750\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1258750</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"503e9e8ccc0680945664a89eee006db1ddabddcc","tid":1259963,"uid":37055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:30:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1a42505941611177f1f62e071ddaea7f347a35b","tid":1259963,"uid":37055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:38:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb9f8b4c870019e2b1ac6a003cbd49d540c24bcf","tid":1259963,"uid":37055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:40:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"970bd8e0431986e1dea1b183cf2b334be6d67111","tid":1259963,"uid":261357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:40:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"347c8052435535880e3d381522df81461d88030e","tid":1259963,"uid":268383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:40:34.000Z","msg":"Oh..no...咁我地可以點？"},{"pid":"4fcd2e16d99f274082fff80d17adb6d20b7ba21f","tid":1259963,"uid":37055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:40:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c8ae723255ed90df0fa5e0a24b59273d7675ed1","tid":1259963,"uid":160728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:40:45.000Z","msg":"推"},